    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and pulls strongly, while the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only minor signs of regular use. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, though you may find a few small stone chips or light surface scratches consistent with its age. It is a dependable, road-ready car that requires no immediate repairs.",
