      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a definitive 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Laguna Seca Blue, maintained to a concours standard. This example features the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing for immediate throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with a precise throw and a robust clutch engagement. Most importantly, the critical 'Big Three' have been addressed: rod bearings replaced with VAC coated bearings, a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement utilizing a structural foam and plate kit, and a complete VANOS overhaul. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by fresh bushings and a limited-slip M Variable Differential Lock. The exterior finish exhibits zero orange peel or rock chips, while the interior leather maintains its original matte texture without bolster wear. Mechanically flawless and historically documented.",
